{"title":"工人忙","authors":["李进才"],"dates":[{"year":1949,"month":3,"day":23}],"parts":[{"type":"paragraph","text":"工人忙"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"（平汉铁路工人李进才）"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"工人忙，工人忙，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"团结起来有力量。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"解放全国已不远，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"发展交通更要忙。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"想起当年反动派，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"不由得人泪汪汪。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"反动派，丧天良，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"不管工人死与活，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"七折八扣发薪饷。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"工人吃穿都不够，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"贪官一买黄金多少两。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"×　　　×　　　×"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"工友们，好喜欢，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"好容易才解放！"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"自己当了家，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"再忙也应当。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"修铁路，架桥梁，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"努力加工修车辆。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"工友们，喜洋洋，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"欢欢喜喜把工上。"}],"comments":[],"comment_pivots":[],"description":"","page_start":4,"page_end":4}